The paper discusses the value of targeting data in online advertising, which involves game-theoretic considerations and optimization of bids. This suggests that the paper could belong to the Game Theory (cs.GT), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA), or Computational Economics and Finance (cs.CE) sub-categories.
